INSERT INTO `ragas_evaluations` VALUES (31,'What are the incident reporting requirements in the Security Policy of Turabit LLC?','Users must report any suspected or confirmed security incidents immediately to the IT or Information Security team, and employees are required to report incidents within 24 hours of detection for prompt investigation and response.',NULL,0.726,0.9699,0.8644,0.9,'custom','2026-03-25 11:00:29'),(32,'What are the responsibilities of employees regarding reporting loss or damage of company-issued equipment at Turabit LLC?','Employees must report any loss, theft, or damage of company equipment to their manager and the IT or administration department within 24 hours of becoming aware of the incident, and they must complete a formal incident report documenting the circumstances.',NULL,0.726,0.9699,0.8644,0.9,'custom','2026-03-25 11:00:29'),(33,'What are the reporting procedures for employees who experience or witness harassment at Turabit LLC?','Employees can report harassment to their manager, HR, or through an anonymous channel, and reports should be made as soon as possible. HR will then conduct a confidential and impartial investigation, document the findings, and follow up with the complainant while ensuring no retaliation occurs.',NULL,0.726,0.9699,0.8644,0.9,'custom','2026-03-25 11:00:29'),(34,'What are the key financial control requirements for approving and managing financial transactions at ABC Technologies Pvt. Ltd.?','All financial transactions must receive prior approval from designated authorities, segregation of duties must be maintained so no individual can both initiate and approve transactions, and all transactions must be accurately recorded, documented, and periodically reviewed to ensure compliance and prevent fraud.',NULL,0.726,0.9699,0.8644,0.9,'custom','2026-03-25 11:00:29'),(35,'What are the rules for logo usage according to the Turbait LLC Brand Guidelines?','The Turbait LLC logo must always be used in its original form without distortion, rotation, or color alteration, with adequate clear space around it, and it must not be stretched, modified, or combined with other elements without prior approval.',NULL,0.726,0.9699,0.8644,0.9,'custom','2026-03-25 11:00:29'),(46,'What is the approval process required for employees to start or modify a remote work arrangement at Turabit LLC?','Employees must submit a formal remote work request to their direct manager including the proposed duration and location, and it must be approved by both the direct manager and the department head. Any changes to the remote work location also require prior approval.','Remote Work Policy',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(47,'What happens when a user exceeds the API rate limit at Turabit LLC?','When a user exceeds the API rate limit, additional requests are automatically rejected and an HTTP 429 error response is returned. Repeated violations may result in temporary throttling, restricted access, or suspension of the API key.','API Rate Limiting Policy',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(48,'What are the requirements for employees when expressing personal opinions about the company on social media?','Employees must clearly distinguish personal opinions from official company positions and include a disclaimer such as \'The views expressed are my own and do not represent the views of my employer\' when discussing company-related topics.','Social Media Policy',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(49,'What are the key components included in the scope of the Turabit Cloud Security Platform implementation for NovaTech Solutions Inc.?','The scope includes deployment and configuration of the Turabit platform, integration with existing systems and cloud infrastructure, security monitoring setup and policy configuration, user access setup with role-based permissions, and initial onboarding and training for client teams.','Sales Proposal Template',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(50,'What are the obligations of the receiving party regarding the use and handling of confidential information under the NDA?','The receiving party must use the confidential information solely for evaluating the potential partnership, ensure confidentiality is maintained by employees and advisors, implement appropriate security measures, and return or destroy the information within 30 days upon request.','Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA)',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(51,'What are the key development practices required to ensure accessibility in Turbait products?','Developers must use semantic HTML, ensure full keyboard navigation, implement ARIA attributes where appropriate, maintain proper focus management, and test for compatibility with screen readers such as JAWS and NVDA.','Turbait Product Accessibility Guidelines',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(52,'What is the primary purpose of the AI-Powered Workflow Recommendation Engine in the Turbait AI Data Automation Platform?','The primary purpose is to enhance user experience by providing AI-driven workflow recommendations based on historical data and usage patterns, reducing manual configuration time and optimizing automation processes.','Product Requirements Document (PRD) for AI-Powered Workflow Recommendation Engine',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:05'),(53,'What were the main user challenges identified in the User Research Report for the Turbait AI Data Automation Platform?','Users struggled with configuring complex workflows, faced limited customization options in the analytics dashboard, and experienced inconsistent integration reliability with external systems.','User Research Report',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:06'),(54,'What are the eligibility requirements for employees to access benefits at Turbait Technologies Pvt. Ltd?','Employees must complete their probation period to be eligible for benefits and must access the HR portal for enrollment and management.','Benefits Guide',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:06'),(55,'What are the key preconditions required before executing a database migration at DataCore Technologies Pvt. Ltd.?','Key preconditions include completing and verifying a full database backup, reviewing and approving migration scripts, conducting testing in a staging environment, validating data integrity and constraints, informing stakeholders of the migration schedule, and ensuring monitoring tools are configured.','Database Migration SOP',0.9181,0.9645,0.9522,0.975,'default','2026-03-25 11:04:06'),(56,'What is the approval process required for employees to start or modify a remote work arrangement at Turabit LLC?','Employees must submit a formal remote work request to their direct manager including the proposed duration and location, and it must be approved by both the direct manager and the department head. Any changes to the remote work location also require prior approval.',NULL,0.8533,0.9746,0.8044,0.8933,'custom','2026-03-26 05:35:59'),(57,'What are the key phases in the incident response process at ABC Technologies Pvt. Ltd?','The incident response process includes detection and alerting, incident logging, classification and prioritization, assignment, investigation and diagnosis, containment, resolution and recovery, communication, closure, and post-incident review.',NULL,0.8533,0.9746,0.8044,0.8933,'custom','2026-03-26 05:35:59'),(58,'What are the key steps involved in the recovery process in the Backup & Recovery Procedure?','The recovery process includes identifying the required backup version, notifying stakeholders, restoring data to a staging environment, validating data integrity and completeness, restoring data to the production environment, and monitoring system performance after recovery.',NULL,0.8533,0.9746,0.8044,0.8933,'custom','2026-03-26 05:35:59'),(59,'What are the consumer rights supported by DataNest Solutions Inc. under the CCPA?','DataNest Solutions Inc. supports the right to know, right to delete, right to opt-out, right to correct, and right to limit the use of personal information, allowing consumers to access, manage, and control their personal data.',NULL,0.8533,0.9746,0.8044,0.8933,'custom','2026-03-26 05:35:59'),(60,'What are the main areas covered in the Data Security Training Guide at Turbait Technologies Pvt. Ltd?','The training guide covers data classification, password management, phishing awareness, device security, remote work security, and incident reporting to ensure employees can protect sensitive data and maintain system integrity.',NULL,0.8533,0.9746,0.8044,0.8933,'custom','2026-03-26 05:35:59'),(61,'What is the approval process required for employees to start or modify a remote work arrangement at Turabit LLC?','Employees must submit a formal remote work request to their direct manager including the proposed duration and location, and it must be approved by both the direct manager and the department head. Any changes to the remote work location also require prior approval.',NULL,0.854,0.9746,0.7933,0.86,'custom','2026-03-26 10:12:46'),(62,'What are the key phases in the incident response process at ABC Technologies Pvt. Ltd?','The incident response process includes detection and alerting, incident logging, classification and prioritization, assignment, investigation and diagnosis, containment, resolution and recovery, communication, closure, and post-incident review.',NULL,0.854,0.9746,0.7933,0.86,'custom','2026-03-26 10:12:46'),(63,'What are the key steps involved in the recovery process in the Backup & Recovery Procedure?','The recovery process includes identifying the required backup version, notifying stakeholders, restoring data to a staging environment, validating data integrity and completeness, restoring data to the production environment, and monitoring system performance after recovery.',NULL,0.854,0.9746,0.7933,0.86,'custom','2026-03-26 10:12:46'),(64,'What are the consumer rights supported by DataNest Solutions Inc. under the CCPA?','DataNest Solutions Inc. supports the right to know, right to delete, right to opt-out, right to correct, and right to limit the use of personal information, allowing consumers to access, manage, and control their personal data.',NULL,0.854,0.9746,0.7933,0.86,'custom','2026-03-26 10:12:46'),(65,'What are the main areas covered in the Data Security Training Guide at Turbait Technologies Pvt. Ltd?','The training guide covers data classification, password management, phishing awareness, device security, remote work security, and incident reporting to ensure employees can protect sensitive data and maintain system integrity.',NULL,0.854,0.9746,0.7933,0.86,'custom','2026-03-26 10:12:46'),(66,'What are the incident reporting requirements in the Security Policy of Turabit LLC?','Users must report any suspected or confirmed security incidents immediately to the IT or Information Security team, and employees are required to report incidents within 24 hours of detection for prompt investigation and response.',NULL,0.7452,0.9699,0.9244,0.9,'custom','2026-03-27 09:42:47'),(67,'What are the responsibilities of employees regarding reporting loss or damage of company-issued equipment at Turabit LLC?','Employees must report any loss, theft, or damage of company equipment to their manager and the IT or administration department within 24 hours of becoming aware of the incident, and they must complete a formal incident report documenting the circumstances.',NULL,0.7452,0.9699,0.9244,0.9,'custom','2026-03-27 09:42:47'),(68,'What are the reporting procedures for employees who experience or witness harassment at Turabit LLC?','Employees can report harassment to their manager, HR, or through an anonymous channel, and reports should be made as soon as possible. HR will then conduct a confidential and impartial investigation, document the findings, and follow up with the complainant while ensuring no retaliation occurs.',NULL,0.7452,0.9699,0.9244,0.9,'custom','2026-03-27 09:42:47'),(69,'What are the key financial control requirements for approving and managing financial transactions at ABC Technologies Pvt. Ltd.?','All financial transactions must receive prior approval from designated authorities, segregation of duties must be maintained so no individual can both initiate and approve transactions, and all transactions must be accurately recorded, documented, and periodically reviewed to ensure compliance and prevent fraud.',NULL,0.7452,0.9699,0.9244,0.9,'custom','2026-03-27 09:42:47'),(70,'What are the rules for logo usage according to the Turbait LLC Brand Guidelines?','The Turbait LLC logo must always be used in its original form without distortion, rotation, or color alteration, with adequate clear space around it, and it must not be stretched, modified, or combined with other elements without prior approval.',NULL,0.7452,0.9699,0.9244,0.9,'custom','2026-03-27 09:42:47');
